Subject: {{group.name}} collective {{month}} report

{{> header}}

<style>

h1 {
  font-weight:normal;
}

h2 {
  margin-top: 30px;
  color:#75cc1f;
  font-weight:normal;
}

ul {
  padding-left: 20px;
}

ul li {
  margin: 5px 0px;
}
.counter {
  font-size: 36px;
  color: #7FADF2;
}
.delta {
  color: #7A7B82;
}
.label {

}
.reimbursed {
  color: #7A7B82;
}
</style>

<div style="font-size:10pt">

<h1>{{group.name}} {{month}} report</h1>

<p>Hi there! This your monthly report for your open collective with your latest balance (as of the last day of last month) and all the expenses that were submitted.
 Don't hesitate to send us your feedback by replying to this email. You can always visit your collective page to get the latest up to date data: <a href="{{group.publicUrl}}">{{group.publicUrl}}</a></p>

<center>
<table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=300 style="margin: 30px 0px">
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="counter">{{{currency group.balance currency=group.currency}}}</span></td>
    <td width=200>&nbsp;</td>
    <td align="center"><span class="counter">{{group.backersCount}}</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="label">current balance</span></td>
    <td></td>
    <td align="center" nowrap><span class="label">total backers</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="delta">({{{sign group.balanceDelta}}}{{{currency group.balanceDelta currency=group.currency}}})</span></span></td>
    <td></td>
    <td align="center"><span class="delta">({{{sign group.backersCountDelta}}}{{group.backersCountDelta}})</span></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br />
<a href="{{group.publicUrl}}#backers"><img src="{{group.publicUrl}}/backers.png?avatarHeight=48&maxWidth=600&button=false&order=recent" /></a>
<a href="{{group.publicUrl}}#sponsors"><img src="{{group.publicUrl}}/sponsors.png?avatarHeight=48&maxWidth=600&button=false&order=recent" /></a>
</center>

<h2>Expenses</h2>
<table width="100%" border=0>

{{#each group.expenses}}
  <tr>
    <td>{{{moment createdAt format="MM/DD"}}}</td>
    <td align="right">{{{currency netAmountInGroupCurrency currency=currency}}}</td>
    <td><a href="{{@root.config.host.app}}/groups/{{@root.group.id}}/expenses/{{id}}">{{description}}</a></td>
    <td class="{{toLowerCase status}}">{{toLowerCase status}}</td>
  </tr>
{{else}}
  No expense submitted. <a href="{{@root.group.publicUrl}}/expenses/new">Submit an expense</a>
{{/each}}
</table>

{{#if topBackers}}
<h2>Recent sponsor activity on Open Collective</h2>
<ul>
{{#each topBackers}}
  <li><a href="{{website}}">{{name}}</a> gave {{{donationsString}}}</li>
{{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

{{#if group.related}}
  <h2>Check out similar collectives</h2>
  <ul>
  {{#each group.related}}
    <li><a href="{{publicUrl}}?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport">{{name}}</a>, on a mission to {{mission}} [<a href="{{publicUrl}}?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport#support">support them!</a>]</li>
  {{/each}}
  </ul>
{{/if}}

<h2>Featured collective</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://opencollective.com/sfartandfilm?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport">San Francisco Art & Film for Teenagers</a>, is on a mission to make all the arts an important part of young people's lives. [<a href="https://opencollective.com/FreeRideToVote?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport#support">support that mission!</a>]</li>
</ul>

<h2>Blog posts</h2>
<li><a href="http://empathia.agency">Empathia Agency</a> (who works with us) is giving back to the open source community. They decided to add 1% to their bills to donate to the Open Source Collective + 1% coming from their margin. <a href="https://medium.empathia.agency/believe-in-giving-back-b451887d79cb#.5j4bysm00">Read more</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://blog.idonethis.com/open-source-community/">How iDoneThis says thank you to the open source community</a></li>
</ul>

<h2>Changelog</h2>
<ul>
<li>Check out our <a href="https://opencollective.com/discover">discovery page</a> with featured collectives and sponsors</li>
<li>Apply for sponsorship. You can now contact existing sponsors on Open Collective to apply for sponsorship. See at the bottom of their profile page, e.g. <a href="https://opencollective.com/digitalocean">DigitalOcean</a>, <a href="https://opencollective.com/iDoneThis">iDoneThis</a>, <a href="https://opencollective.com/saucelabs">SauceLabs</a> and <a href="https://opencollective.com/saucelabs">SauceLabs</a></li>
</ul>

</div>

{{> footer}}